<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Poems</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Georgia", serif;
      background-color: #0d0d0d;
      color: #d6d6d6;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 60px 30px;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: normal;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .tagline {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      margin-bottom: 80px;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .poem {
      margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    p {
      white-space: pre-line;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 120px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #555;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Poems</h1>
<div class="tagline">A place for words that didn’t survive silence.</div>

<div class="poem">
  <div class="title">Untitled</div>
  <p>
I learned
that silence is not empty—

it is full
of things that refused to stay.
  </p>
</div>

<footer>
  © Emmanuel — all words kept intact.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
